          <div class="p-4">
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Hairline Restoration</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">SMP micropigmentation for natural hair follicle impressions.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$680</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">2–3 sessions</p></div><a href="/book/" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-all border border-neutral-200">
          <div class="relative h-32 overflow-hidden"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521590832167-7bcbfaa6381f?w=400&h=300&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Scalp Therapy" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300" loading="lazy" /><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent"></div></div>
          <div class="p-4">
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Scalp Therapy</h3>
