            <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mb-3">Classic, hybrid, volume &amp; mega volume styles.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between"><div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-primary-600">$153</p><p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">2 hr | Fills $43</p></div><a href="/book/" class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-primary-600 text-white text-xs font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors">Book</a></div>
